{"tid":1615392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不要說偽勇武 試著說新前線","createTime":"2019-10-03T05:35:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T07:13:08.000Z","uid":255749,"like":38,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"fb940d8a3800707e5c2afd9e258e72178676bdbe","tid":1615392,"uid":255749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T05:35:35.000Z","msg":"呢幾日見到好多post講偽勇武<br />\n主要都係指有班手足著哂full gear但係狗一推就雞飛狗走<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都真係見到前線有好大嘅分別<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但兩個月之後呢班人唔見哂<br />\n都明嘅勇武仔仔係以前嘅戰役入面有幾多可以全身以退<br />\n仲要隨時比人打都無到再出嚟<br />\n但同時兩個月之後都多左好多人更加想上前<br />\n所以佢地會開始買gear同埋嘗試做更多容易啲嘅工作<br />\n例如滅煙小隊人數大幅上升<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多時候佢地都係單拖或者兩三個為一組<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就住呢個情況，勇武可考慮新轉型同新崗位<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 不打陣地戰，打游擊戰</span></strong></span><br />\n呢個主要係因為夠膽埋身肉搏既真勇武少左<br />\n而popo經過呢個幾月開始更加識得佈陣<br />\n再加埋黨鐵同商場加持令佢地可以先佔據有利位置<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地好多時都處於下風非常被動<br />\n打陣地戰其實無著數<br />\n反而組成小隊打游擊<br />\n針對一啲有象徵性嘅空間例如黨鐵、建制派議員辦事處、政府合署<br />\n武力先能夠用得其所<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之於平時，又有老豆搵仔，大家識做啦<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">2. 前線唔駛做滅煙隊</span></span></strong><br />\n後面會有好多人backup你<br />\n如果你敢企第一排直接面對popo<br />\n咁你可以進化為水系火系魔法師<br />\n係時候搵人組隊打怪獸<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3. 大家嘅覺悟要進化</span></span></strong><br />\n咩係勇武？唔係著哂gear cosplay就叫勇武呀<br />\n勇武可以係一種心態 為左革命有被捕甚至犧牲嘅覺悟<br />\n但更重要係行動上<br />\n勇武相信暴力係迫使政權回應訴求嘅重要途徑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能好多和理岩岩先突破心理關口<br />\n但政權暴力程度上升得咁快<br />\n大家再唔進化就只係用緊勇武嘅血汗嚟做活人祭祀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n換取自己可以苟且偷生嘅日子<br />\n<br />\n講好左不割蓆不篤灰不分化<br />\n所以不要說偽勇武<br />\n試著說新前線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一日中共仲係到一日都係港殤<br />\n大家要繼續進化<br />\nkeep住賀佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"96134138fbe9b0fd36e1334873805de01acc21fe","tid":1615392,"uid":255749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T05:36:08.000Z","msg":"自推十連 1/10"},{"pid":"faf787718507c0ec90fe47dc32508a354d9603a5","tid":1615392,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T05:36:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0b062cf3db174a5c641b2a96addc4bf5383e31de","tid":1615392,"uid":255749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T05:36:21.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"a5124d3e3e39127b443d6422c0e2f9bea2649f9c","tid":1615392,"uid":255749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T05:36:32.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"26a7404cb0e64239a505fe79a2e09b7dc019cebe","tid":1615392,"uid":255749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T05:36:44.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"0ab76e93e1461bea7dd4e5a72f02d1e3e1765cb9","tid":1615392,"uid":255749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T05:36:56.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"4393f71faad7ce96c5986d22547557f4643ed76c","tid":1615392,"uid":255749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T05:37:06.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"cbbf0f9f67bf6a9c5aa20631f0ba484b7d328ad0","tid":1615392,"uid":255749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T05:37:30.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"71d886047e64aa345af0d67685f126acf78f8595","tid":1615392,"uid":255749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T05:37:40.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"b7f533e1723bdb6dbc5e1b9fc5997897058d2003","tid":1615392,"uid":23818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T05:37:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"42faa71748af93cbf42cf4054808713de7e30ab2","tid":1615392,"uid":255749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T05:37:51.000Z","msg":"9/10"},{"pid":"d9ece22c174ff78ba6251de4159fd9e7487aa32f","tid":1615392,"uid":255749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T05:38:05.000Z","msg":"10/10"},{"pid":"ea3eefcc3e5720fbfbd45c1bfc9c9f81048a1cf6","tid":1615392,"uid":270687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T05:38:54.000Z","msg":"推唔郁"},{"pid":"0d02479d9cb44c00b0c0161439917ee289d610e6","tid":1615392,"uid":276783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T05:40:01.000Z","msg":"推唔郁但G持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0465e470c39e3e00ce30701f1ec57328a422994","tid":1615392,"uid":82655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T05:40:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1e71d01f8c62a9d53f9a7ab97c4d531c82144b30","tid":1615392,"uid":82655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T05:41:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1868c1fbccc78f72186cb78d3164cd813270ce1b","tid":1615392,"uid":270277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T05:41:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"911d4ddfc7c75539f168074eb9357166af71c2d5","tid":1615392,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T05:41:36.000Z","msg":"Full Armor 和理非"},{"pid":"0c564d93ac2b5db1f092bad3356134322435314e","tid":1615392,"uid":82655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T05:43:17.000Z","msg":"其實和理非都可以幫手做結界師之類嘅職業"},{"pid":"d40c5a7d97de37f752108024d1eb751ef1cdc52f","tid":1615392,"uid":11374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T05:43:19.000Z","msg":"新前線進化煙霧隊<br />\n<br />\n真勇可以轉職做法師 同足球員"},{"pid":"7c13eee1d7084ea6f17c58e75e5294291e07ceb0","tid":1615392,"uid":28818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T05:43:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5ee7c3b05dfe5db9cd570979a08daa31dfa64f6","tid":1615392,"uid":40137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T05:43:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9bde1c331ebcd13245935b02e68f34a5db8c178","tid":1615392,"uid":178944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T05:44:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">加油新勇武</span></span>"},{"pid":"bb1f5926b6c201ee7c74f5a9ee79c0eb943422f1","tid":1615392,"uid":40137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T05:44:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}